      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question. i got prescribed this antibiotic for a skin infection last week and im on day 3 now. the redness and swelling are basically totally gone and i feel 100% fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? dont really wanna keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to.",
