    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it just feels unnecessary since the skin looks totally normal now. like, if the infection is gone, why keep killing good bacteria too? my friend said that if you feel better, the medicine has already done its job and the rest is just extra stuff the body has to process. is there any actual medical reason why i HAVE to finish them if the symptoms are 100% gone?",
