      "content": "but i already finished the main part and the inflammation is totally gone. it feels like i'm just taking drugs for no reason now. wouldn't it be safer for my gut health and my immune system to just stop before I cause more issues with the balance of my microbiome? it just seems like the risk of the infection coming back is way smaller than the risk of taking unnecessary medicine.",
